{"tid":584859,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知點解上水成日塞車？就係因為好多車呀！","createTime":"2018-03-08T06:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T11:33:32.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"edf9f9bab29f7d3dc04aac46e3299885f7808bbe","tid":584859,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/145830_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F145830_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6e400e54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a726fe581ee17b5de9b5647aa7246d609a01df2","tid":584859,"uid":53698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:02:36.000Z","msg":"開心大發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ab512fa76de366676f4833bbc7cb02edaf8914","tid":584859,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"太少行車綫"},{"pid":"e7d5e86463e27d0b5b4400e783a69c8a85b72d63","tid":584859,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"起多幾條路囉"},{"pid":"822a9a35821d75c0bc958188f249b0cc4698fe57","tid":584859,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:29:08.000Z","msg":"多咗咩人會買車，大家心照啦"},{"pid":"67d64e0c57de9c70fc2a2e5e7985178c4aaebca5","tid":584859,"uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/193256_ce482636e4782ce6d80f02cd83235d80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F193256_ce482636e4782ce6d80f02cd83235d80.png&h=f5fe9f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【簡明北區塞車主因】<br />\n最近，有位議員話北區塞車嘅主因係因爲多車。唔少人直指此說法太廢，眞係「鬼唔知阿媽係女人」。雖然多車的確係原因，但係講唔出重點。<br />\n<br />\n造成北區經常大塞車原因，係道路設計問題。粉嶺公路兩個迴旋處無法消化過多嘅車流量，導致車流倒灌返入公路；形成連貫塞車。其中雞嶺迴旋處、掃管埔路、新運路、百和路嘅道路設計亦係造成塞車嘅元兇。<br />\n<br />\n迴旋處係唔少新新市鎭嘅早期產物，四處都可以見到。迴旋處嘅好處係比較慳位、造價亦比大型交匯處平。但係呢類迴旋處祇能處理中小量交通流量，一旦發生意外，亦會造成大塞車；因爲連接太多支路，無法卽時疏導。然而港府發展北區時亦低估新市鎭人口增長，電氣化火車逼爗經已係例子。所以明顯睇得出，北區兩個迴旋處嘅設計亦低估車流量。失敗例子仲有元朗博愛交匯處。<br />\n<br />\n如果要長遠解決塞車問題，就必須先要向迴旋處落手。可以將雞嶺迴旋處改成 Diverging Diamond Interchange 或 Single Point Urban Interchange。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RoadResearch/photos/a.1253458658012550.1073741827.1252628151428934/2052540378104370/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRoadResearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.1253458658012550.1073741827.1252628151428934%2F2052540378104370%2F&d=KQPkIZW%2B%2FEF3KFCtQifZAzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=827cbd5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RoadResearch/photos/a.1253458658012550.1073741827.1252628151428934/2052540378104370/</a>"}]}